# Next.js 15 & TypeScript Development Patterns

## Project Architecture

### Next.js 15 App Router Structure
Follow the established directory structure in [src/app/](mdc:src/app/):

```typescript
// App Router file organization
src/app/
├── layout.tsx          // Root layout with providers
├── page.tsx           // Home page
├── admin/             // Admin-only routes
│   ├── page.tsx      // Admin dashboard
│   ├── assignments/  // Assignment management
│   └── question-bank/ // Question bank management
├── api/              // API routes
│   ├── auth/         // Authentication endpoints
│   ├── assignments/  // Assignment CRUD
│   └── question-bank/ // Question bank CRUD
└── assignments/      // Student assignment pages
    └── [id]/         // Dynamic assignment routes
```

